DTSTART:20260615T230000Z
DESCRIPTION:HCP Members are invited to join our June Critique Group led by 
	Fernando Castro\, Curator\, Sicardi Ayers Bacino. You may register for fre
	e as a Presenter and get feedback on your work from Castro and fellow HCP 
	members\, or as an Attendee and partake in the discussion. Our critique gr
	oups provide a supportive and professional environment to share your work 
	and take the next step.Please visit our Critique Groups page for more info
	rmation.\n\nhttps://www.edu.hcponline.org/events/summer26-critique-group\n
